name: DynamicTriggerEvents

properties.name: ON_PAGE_LOAD
properties.description: target is triggered on loading of the page.

properties.name: ON_PAGE_CLICK
properties.description: target is triggered on clicking on the page.

properties.name: ON_STATE_LOAD
properties.description: target is triggered on loading of the state in a multi-state object.

properties.name: ON_CLICK
properties.description: target is triggered on a button or self click.

properties.name: ON_ROLLOVER
properties.description: target is triggered on a button or self rollover.

properties.name: ON_RELEASE
properties.description: target is triggered on a button release.

properties.name: ON_ROLLOFF
properties.description: target is triggered on a button rolloff.

properties.name: ON_SELF_CLICK
properties.description: target is triggered on self click.

properties.name: ON_SELF_ROLLOVER
properties.description: target is triggered on self rollover.

description: The event that triggers a list of dynamic target objects to play.
